title: Lynda - Outlook for Mac First Look with Nick Brazzi
description:
[b]Lynda - Outlook for Mac First Look with Nick Brazzi[/b] 
24m 52s Appropriate for all Nov 03, 2014 | Uploaded in Nov 20, 2014 by 2boweb

Subjects:    Business Email 
Software:    Outlook for Mac, Office for Mac, Office 365, 



Office for Mac won't arrive until 2015, but (surprise!) the new Outlook is available now for Office 365 subscribers. Get a first look at the new interface and enhanced feature set in Outlook for Mac in this course with Nick Brazzi. He'll cover installing and setting up the software from an Office 365 account, as well as sending and receiving mail, issuing calendar invites, and working with contacts, tasks, and notes
